# 🍎 FreshMart - E-Commerce Fruit Store

## ⚡ About This Project
FreshMart is a modern, responsive frontend e-commerce website for a fresh fruit store.  
It is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to simulate a real-world online shopping experience with product listings, cart system UI, and checkout design.

This project focuses on **UI design, responsive layout, and frontend development skills**.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
